  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Rail Gun</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Small brown- and gray-skinned rodents, the <span
  class=3DSpellE>Jintus</span> often get themselves in some form of conflic=
t, however
  they are not very enthusiastic about fighting. They will often draw in th=
eir
  allies to fight their own battles, using their chosen friends as the
  intimidation factor in any war.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Jintus</span> favor races t=
hey
  consider to be strong and able to win wars for them.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Living and hunting in packs, pack feuds and wars are
  common. Hunting is a sport they are obsessed with. Many <span class=3DSpe=
llE>Jintus</span>
  will lose their lives hunting the <span class=3DSpellE>Terrellion</span>,=
 a
  dangerous predator from their <span class=3DSpellE>homeworld</span> 10 ti=
mes
  the size of the average <span class=3DSpellE>Jintus</span>.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Jintus</span> inhabit caves and=
 other
  natural or intelligently made shelters of ice worlds. Not very good engin=
eers
  they will kill or drive out occupants of these potential habitats to find
  warm homes.</p>
